schools.name: Lemon Grove Academy For The Sciences And Humanities

data.description: Beautiful single-story home situated on a quiet street in an established Lemon Grove neighborhood. This home has 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms and has a perfect layout for entertaining! Features include upgraded kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, wood and tile flooring throughout, an oversized family room and a low maintenance completely renovated front and back yard complete with turf, concrete and a sparkling pool. No neighbors on the backside and plenty of seating room for your guests. This home also has a 23 solar panel system to help save on utility bills along with pool solar to extend your pool season! This home is conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, freeways and top notch schools!
